{"article_id":"UEt9k7QXjbFUwo97","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"In a sudden announcement","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that caught Catholics around the world off guard ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"Pope Benedict XVI said","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"he will resign at the end of February ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"becoming the first pontiff","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"to step down in nearly 600 years .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"The 85-year-old pontiff made the announcement Monday ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"he no longer had the strength","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"to carry out his papal duties .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"`` After having repeatedly examined my conscience before God ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"I have come to the certainty","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"that my strengths , due to an advanced age , are no longer suited to an adequate exercise of the Petrine ministry , ''","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"the pope said","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"according to a statement","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"released by the Vatican .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"He said","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"he is aware of the `` seriousness '' of his resignation ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"but that he did so in `` full freedom . ''","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"He will live out his days on Vatican grounds ,","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"according to officials .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"The last pope","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"to resign","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"was Pope Gregory XII ,","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"who stepped down in 1415 in a deal","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"to end the Great Western Schism among competing papal claimants .","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"The sudden announcement sets the stage","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"for the Vatican to hold a conclave","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"to elect a new pope by mid-March ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"since the traditional mourning time","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"that would follow the death of a pope","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"does n't have to be observed .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"There are several papal contenders in the wings , but no obvious front-runner ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"according to Vatican watchers .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"A Vatican spokesperson told `` Fox & Friends ''","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"that Pope Benedict `` will not take part in conclave ''","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"to choose his successor .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Officials hope","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"to have a new pope in place in time for the start of Holy Week , on March 14 .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"Although there has been much speculation about Pope Benedict 's health ,","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"a Vatican spokesman said","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"he is not in any immediate danger .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"`` There 's nothing immediately serious or grave , ''","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"the Vatican spokesman told ABC .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"The pope 's 89-year-old brother , Georg Ratzinger , told a German news agency","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"that the pope has had difficulty walking recently","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"and has considered stepping down for months .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"\" His age is weighing on him , \"","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Georg Ratzinger said .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"\" At this age my brother wants more rest . \"","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"Fox News Executive Vice President John Moody , former Vatican bureau chief for Time magazine , told Fox News Channel","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"that Pope Benedict showed courage","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"by accepting","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"that the rigors of the papacy had become too much for him .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"`` I think","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"it is one of the bravest things","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"I ' ve ever heard of , ''","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"said Moody ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"who is author of a 1996 biography of Pope John Paul II .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"`` Nobody gives up power willingly .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Nobody gives up power","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"without forethought .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"For this man ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"who really the world hasn ' t gotten to know very well ,","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"despite the fact","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"that he ' s been around as pope for seven years ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"to do this speaks volumes about the kind of man he is","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"and the kind of leader of the church","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"that he insisted on being . ''","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"Born Joseph Aloisius Ratzinger ,","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"Pope Benedict became the 265th pope","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"after being elected by his fellow cardinals on April 19 , 2005 , at the age of 78","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"following the death of the popular John Paul II .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"The ninth German pope and first in nearly 500 years , Benedict was ordained in 1951","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"and was a major figure at the Vatican stage for decades before his ascension .","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"Ratzinger chose the name Benedict ,","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"which comes from the Latin word","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"meaning `` the blessed , ''","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"in homage to Pope Benedict XV ,","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"who was pope during World War I ,","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"and Saint Benedict of Nursia ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"who established the Benedictine monasteries .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"During his papacy and in the years prior , Benedict was a key figure in the church 's efforts","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"to address widespread instances of sexual abuse of children by priests .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"In 2001 , then-Cardinal Ratzinger convinced John Paul II to put the Congregation for the Doctrine of the Faith ,","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"which he led ,","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"in charge","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"of investigating cases and setting policy regarding what he termed `` filth '' in the church .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"As a cardinal , Ratzinger pushed through important reforms ,","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"including making Internet offenses against children a violation","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"covered by canon law ,","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"extending child abuse offenses to include the sexual abuse of all under 18 ,","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"waiving of the statute of limitation","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"and speeding the process","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"of dismissing guilty priests .","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"Even before becoming pope ,","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"Ratzinger had experienced health problems","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"and attempted to resign from his role as prefect of the Congregation for the Doctrine of Faith several times ,","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"only to stay on at the behest of Pope John Paul II .","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"In 1991 , Ratzinger suffered a stroke ,","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"according to reports .","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"After becoming pope ,","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"Benedict ,","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"who predicted a short tenure for himself ,","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"suffered another stroke in May 2005 ,","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"according to the Vatican .","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"He is also believed to suffer from a heart condition .","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"As pope , Benedict embraced technology .","depth":4},{"id":108,"text":"In December , he began using Twitter ,","depth":5},{"id":109,"text":"where he has 1.5 million followers .","depth":5},{"id":110,"text":"`` We must trust in the mighty power of God ' s mercy , ''","depth":5},{"id":111,"text":"read his most recent tweet ,","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"posted yesterday .","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"`` We are all sinners ,","depth":5},{"id":114,"text":"but His grace transforms us","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"and makes us new . ''","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":231,"left":184,"right":230,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":136,"right":183,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":121,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":118,"right":120,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":118,"left":117,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":117,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":3,"right":119,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":130,"right":134,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":124,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":6,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":7,"right":122,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":122,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":127,"right":128,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":126,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":10,"right":125,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":125,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":132,"right":133,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":132,"left":16,"right":131,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":131,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":133,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":140